# Normalize line endings to LF across the repo. The toolchain
# (openapi-typescript, prettier, eslint) emits LF; without this,
# core.autocrlf=true smudges checkouts to CRLF and regenerating committed
# files (e.g. src/shared/api/generated/**) shows spurious EOL-only diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize or diff.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.wasm binary
